{"tid":381844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又係地盤  油壓腳斷裂吊臂車翻側　司機慘遭鐵臂擊斃","createTime":"2017-08-31T09:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T13:15:29.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6a4de62dbbd2d092f9fc757da5b6fd766a52db7","tid":381844,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"長沙灣郝德傑道一個地盤發生工業意外，下午2時許，一名姓高（51歲）吊臂車司機，在地盤外操控吊臂車吊臂，將2輛小型挖泥車吊上車。當他正吊運第2輛挖泥車時，吊臂車右邊的油壓腳突然斷裂，吊臂車向右翻側；高見狀跳車逃生，惟遭車上的挖泥車吊臂擊中頭及胸口，當場重創昏迷倒地。<br />\n<br />\n救護員接報趕至，替高即場急救後再急送明愛醫院搶救，惜延至下午3時許不治。事後有多名親友接報，趕至醫院了解，當得悉噩耗後傷心痛哭。警方及勞工處正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170831/photo/bkn-20170831145513850-0831_00822_001_03b.jpg?20170831170715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170831%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170831145513850-0831_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20170831170715&d=WDMGX52A1KcV%2Fr3RIxTRRp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=1e67399d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170831/photo/bkn-20170831145513850-0831_00822_001_03b.jpg?20170831170715</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170831/bkn-20170831145513850-0831_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170831%2Fbkn-20170831145513850-0831_00822_001.html&d=WDMGX52A1KcV%2Fr3RIxTRRp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=fc21b6cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170831/bkn-20170831145513850-0831_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e1a17647b81473418ae2d4526fbdf83432e31da7","tid":381844,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T09:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170831/photo/bkn-20170831145513850-0831_00822_001_03b.jpg?20170831170715\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170831%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170831145513850-0831_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F2017